keyMappings:
# Qutebrowser keys
# Scrolling
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-f> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-b> scrollFullPageUp

map d removeTab
map u restoreTab

# Extended hint mode
map ;y LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
map ;r LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue

map go Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map gO Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab

# Misc commands
map gC duplicateTab
map gJ moveTabLeft
map gK moveTabRight

map gf toggleViewSource

unmap gs
unmap x
unmap X
unmap yt
unmap <<
unmap >>
unmap ge
unmap gE
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap yf
unmap <a-f>
searchEngines:
w:  https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php?search=%s Arch Linux Wiki
ap: https://anaconda.org/search?q=%s Anaconda
d:  https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s duckduckgo
g: https://github.com/search?q=%s GitHub
gi: https://www.google.com/search?tbm=isch&q=%s
gm: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Maps
gr: https://www.google.com/search?hl=en&tbo=1&tbs=qdr:y&q=%s
l:  https://www.google.com/search?btnI=I'm+Feeling+Lucky&q=%s Lucky
o: https://search.nixos.org/options?channel=unstable&from=0&size=50&sort=relevance&type=packages&query=%s NixOS Options
p: https://search.nixos.org/packages?channel=unstable&size=50&sort=relevance&type=packages&query=%s NixOS Packages
ra: http://dle.rae.es/?w=%s RAE
so: http://stackoverflow.com/search?q=%s StackOverflow
su: http://superuser.com/search?q=%s SuperUser
t:  http://translate.google.com/?source=osdd#auto|auto|%s Translate
te: http://translate.google.com/?source=osdd#auto|en|%s Translate to English
tf: https://translate.google.com/#auto/fr/%s Translate to French
ts: https://translate.google.com/#auto/es/%s Translate to Spanish
wi:  http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Search?search=%s Wikipedia
y:  http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
